<a id="installation"></a>

## Installation

Requires **Python 3.11+**.

```bash
# Isolated install (recommended)
pipx install bijux-cli

# Standard
pip install bijux-cli
```

Upgrade: `pipx upgrade bijux-cli` or `pip install --upgrade bijux-cli`.

[Back to top](#top)

